      <link>http://www.rvsleuth.com/getting-started/</link>
      <comments>http://www.rvsleuth.com/getting-started/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Jul 2010 21:17:58 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>rvwpadmin</dc:creator>
      <category><![CDATA[Uncategorized]]></category>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.rvsleuth.com/?p=66</guid>
      <description>As the economy recovers, America is remembering the RV lifestyle. During the downturn, RV sales suffered. Several major RV manufacturers went under. A couple of others spent time in bankruptcy, but are slowly recovering. The important thing for RVers is that sales are rising again. It will take a while before it reaches the boom [...]&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.rvsleuth.com/getting-started/"&gt;An important resource for RVers&lt;/a&gt; is a post from &lt;a href="http://www.rvsleuth.com"&gt;RV Sleuth&lt;/a&gt;, which teaches RVers how to get the RVs they want for big discounts.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/rv-sleuth/RV_Sleuth-An_important_resource_for_RVers.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p></p><p>As the economy recovers, America is remembering the RV lifestyle.</p>
<p>During the downturn, <a class="ld_link" href="/rv-sales" target=" " title="RV sales">RV sales</a> suffered. Several major <a class="ld_link" href="/rv-manufacturers" target=" " title="RV manufacturers">RV manufacturers</a> went under. A couple of others spent time in bankruptcy, but are slowly recovering.</p>
<p>The important thing for RVers is that sales are rising again. It will take a while before it reaches the boom levels of a couple of years ago. Nevertheless, the industry is strengthening.</p>
<p>That means demand for RVs is picking up. And that means it&#8217;s not as easy to get a good deal as it used to be. </p>
<p>In late 2007 and 2008, dealers were desperate. But not any more. It&#8217;s getting tougher to get a good RV at a good price.</p>
<p>That&#8217;s why I&#8217;m remodeling this site. With a new design, hopefully it will be easier to find everything. It will also be updated more frequently.</p>
<p>Hope you find it useful!</p>
<p><a href="http://www.rvsleuth.com/getting-started/">An important resource for RVers</a> is a post from <a href="http://www.rvsleuth.com">RV Sleuth</a>, which teaches RVers how to get the RVs they want for big discounts.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
